  "3291850": {
    "name": "Scaling Up",
    "steam_appid": 3291850,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为一位蛇农场的主人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291850/extras/0a72f483c2abe42dbb6ebb13fe9aa9fb.avif?t=1770919957\" width=594 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一只小龙，从零开始建设你的蛇农场。收集和管理资源，建造各种设施来安置你的蛇，并确保它们得到照顾，保持快乐，并收集它们美丽的鳞片。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>发现各种迷人的蛇类</strong></h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291850/extras/c845d0331269fa2a8dbc1a9f4d159696.avif?t=1770919957\" width=594 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每座建筑可以容纳不同种类的蛇，每种蛇都会掉落不同的鳞片。这些鳞片可以用来建造新建筑、制作更好的工具和设备，或者卖掉换取黄金。从带角的蛇，到有轮子甚至翅膀的蛇，你将会结交很多爬行的小伙伴。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自动化你的任务</strong> </h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291850/extras/e928fc7183581661560f65e144002309.poster.avif?t=1770919957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291850/extras/e928fc7183581661560f65e144002309.webm?t=1770919957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291850/extras/e928fc7183581661560f65e144002309.mp4?t=1770919957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使是非常有动力和天赋的小龙，也无法独自完成所有事情。大多数蛇种可以帮助你管理农场，包括帮助喂养其他蛇、将鳞片搬运到储存区、砍伐树木、寻找食物、打造新装备，甚至做饭。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>组织远征寻找稀有材料</strong></h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291850/extras/c29a7e2ba7b69f5cef0467ab9339b8d3.avif?t=1770919957\" width=594 height=190 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >派遣你的战斗蛇和收集蛇探索新土地，收集稀有资源和食物。一些地区会在水下或高空，其他地区则可能太热或太冷。给你的探索者装备好，让他们抵御极端天气，或雇佣专业种类来完成任务。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>根据时间、天气和季节变化进行规划</strong></h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291850/extras/2e93b3cc5290ffcde142ef4fd04dbcb7.avif?t=1770919957\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291850/extras_big/2e93b3cc5290ffcde142ef4fd04dbcb7.avif?t=1770919957 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >考虑到时间，确保每天满足你蛇类的需求。准备好应对可能影响蛇类工作天气的变化，以及季节变化带来的新机制。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>研究与开发</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291850/extras/34dc330c9c93283a2924f1485211eb15.avif?t=1770919957\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291850/extras_big/34dc330c9c93283a2924f1485211eb15.avif?t=1770919957 width=800 height=450 /></span>建造一个实验室，在蛇类的帮助下进行研究，解锁新的蛇种、建筑和农场改进。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>装饰并打造属于你的农场</strong></h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291850/extras/ab7a25c4a2d98ea1db1e20498ebff341.apng?t=1770919957\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291850/extras/ab7a25c4a2d98ea1db1e20498ebff341.poster.avif?t=1770919957\" class=\"bb_img\" width=594 height=300 /></picture></span>从各种装饰物品中选择，并为你的农场增添个人风格。扩展农场并不意味着不能让它焕然一新。</p>",
